tuur.name: readme.txt
tuur.text:
README.txt

Welcome to User's Project!
======================

This project is designed for testing purposes.
It contains random data, code snippets, and other useful resources.

Files:
------
- README.txt -> This file, providing an overview of the project.
- sample_code.js -> Contains JavaScript code examples.
- data.csv -> Stores some sample data used for testing.

Usage:
------
1. Clone the repository.
2. Run the provided scripts to test the functionality.
3. Explore the code and make modifications as needed.

Contact:
--------
If you have any questions or issues, please reach out via email or open an issue in the repository.

Enjoy!

guest.name: welcome
guest.text:
WELCOME TO SUBLIMINAL.OS™

This is a space that aims to free it's users from having to carry have equipment. If you have an internet connection, you can use all the power we have to offer for only 1.99$/month!

We are a team of motivated administrators that want to give our users the very best service possible. All of us have a lot of experience in the IT world.
We pride ourselves in our development, data protection, cybersecurity & network skills!

We started this project in 2020 to give people with weak machines and little money to buy a new one the option of using remote devices with a lot of storage space. You are forced to but a completely new device now that you can't even add more storage to your devices, and the option of downloading more RAM also does not work anymore ;-).
But we offer a solution! Internet is everywhere. So you can access our servers from anywhere! 1 TB of storage space included at the lowest price.

PRICES:
1TB - 1.99 $
2TB - 3.49 $
3TB - 4.46 $
More storage can be discussed!

CONTACT
info@subliminal.os
www.subliminal.os

- The Subliminal Team
